{"tid":569764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食環署：拘捕無牌熟食小販 「少人一定拉」","createTime":"2018-02-23T04:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T05:37:19.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fba69873bfa30ca19c19caefc7243360dfcb0c11","tid":569764,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T04:23:43.000Z","msg":"食環署高級衛生主任賴友裕在盤問下指，2015年農曆年同事執勤時遇上滋擾，故翌年策略有變，改為容忍小販在後巷擺賣，而這項改變沒有向公眾公佈。賴又補充，其實過往年廿四至大年初三均會接到行動指令，會拘捕無牌熟食小販，「少人一定拉」，務求收得阻嚇其他小販之效。"},{"pid":"b658607e1a7882b676f3adfffb9afd01472e93c0","tid":569764,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T04:25:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「少人一定拉」</blockquote><br />\n欺善怕惡<br />\n垃圾"},{"pid":"d203e4958550bda8277257e6977ea8d6f4fdaabe","tid":569764,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T04:26:31.000Z","msg":"食環真係最垃圾既部門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c434daf6508db60c33b4adde92a3ff0f3b345d","tid":569764,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}